alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define
Class Status

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define.Status
public class Status
extends java.lang.Object

The Status class is used ot denote the status of an SUnit. A Status can have the following values.

  • NOTDEFINED
  • WAITING
  • READY
  • RUNNING
  • ABORTED
  • COMPLETE
